Trousdale-adjacent, sophisticated and private home, minutes from Beverly Hills shops and restaurants, offers awe inspiring views. This gated, chic hillside home, flooded with natural light, has been totally transformed with the utmost style and attention to detail. Long private driveway with parking for several cars leads to a secluded garden. Living room with vaulted ceilings and breathtaking views. Chef's kitchen has top of the line appliances and center island. Large patio with adjoining gourmet outdoor kitchen. Outdoor space is perfect for al fresco dining, suitable for all entertaining needs. Kitchen opens to family room and wet bar; an expansive great-room for all to enjoy. Upstairs are three generous bedrooms, all with designer en suite bathrooms. Luxurious master suite offers canyon and ocean views. Lower level offers additional private bedroom, bath, office space and full gym. Subterranean 3000 bottle refrigerated wine cellar for the collector or connoisseur. A must-see!

9085 Alto Cedro Dr is a house in Beverly Hills, CA 90210. This 3,800 square foot house sits on a 0.3 acre lot and features 4 bedrooms and 4.5 bathrooms. This house has been listed on Redfin since August 31, 2020 and is currently priced at $2,995,000. This property was built in 1991 and last sold on February 07, 2018 for $2,345,000. Nearby schools include Wonderland Ave Elementary School and Wonderland Avenue Elementary School. The closest grocery store is Laurel Canyon Country Store. Nearby restaurants include Chipotle Mexican Grill and Pace. 9085 Alto Cedro Dr is near Fryman Canyon Park, Laurel Canyon Park and Coldwater Canyon Park. This address can also be written as 9085 Alto Cedro Drive, Beverly Hills, California 90210.
